&lt;h1 id="science-is-an-error-correcting-mechanism"&gt;Science Is an Error-Correcting Mechanism&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Apr 30 2021&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;
Where do good explanations come from?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There&amp;rsquo;s currently an obsession with &lt;strong&gt;induction&lt;/strong&gt;, the idea that you can predict the future from the past. You can say, &amp;ldquo;I saw one, then two, then three, then four, then five, so therefore next must be six, seven, eight, nine.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>